{"tid":601044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【秒爆噴火】強國男網購手機電 一掂即爆全店驚逃","createTime":"2018-03-22T01:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T11:06:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bb487176877a3acc1dc1676070dfe806dacd8c62","tid":601044,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T01:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180322/large/1521648223_7f68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180322%2Flarge%2F1521648223_7f68.jpg&h=1284b038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果自己不懂，千萬不要亂拆手機或自行修理！甘肅平涼市一男子，覺得手機電池的續航力變短，於是在網上自己購買電池，拿到當地一間手機維修店內要求幫忙更換。沒想到這名男子嫌老闆的收費太貴，於是便問老闆借用工具，自行更換。沒想到他打開新電池時，鑷子一下子夾破外殼，電池即時爆炸，噴出熊熊火光，其他顧客即時慌忙逃走。<br />\n<br />\n事發在前日，現場拍攝的閉路電視片段顯示一名身穿紅色外套的男子，椅在手機店的飾櫃上，右手拿着工具，突然他手中的電池爆炸，男子與店內其他4名顧客，馬上奪門而出，走到店外躲避，坐在櫃枱後的老闆，則呆呆站着，看着這一幕。<br />\n<br />\n這名手機店老闆稱，這名紅色外套男子原來是拿着自己買的電池，想幫忙換電，可是，當老闆告訴他收費之後，男子即時說太貴，並向老闆借了一個鑷子，在一邊自己更換。老闆稱，男子拿着鑷子，一下刺穿了新電池，引發爆炸，幸火勢不是很大，事件中無人傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n現在的手機多是使用鋰離子電池，可是鋰離子電池化學性質活躍，十分易燃，甚至會引起爆炸，廠商都會在外殼加上警告標誌，警告消費者不能刺穿、柝解電池，同時亦不建議消費者自己換電。<br />\n<br />\n今年1月內地一名男子，拿着iPhone到一個手機商場想更換電池，當他看到新的電池時，竟然拿起、放入口裏咬了一口，即時引發爆炸，冒出火球及濃煙。這名男子事後聲稱，他是想驗證電池是否真貨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180321/large/1521646601_8fcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180321%2Flarge%2F1521646601_8fcc.jpg&h=de986861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年1月內地一名男子咬穿電池，引發爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180322/57975298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57975298&d=XkRSC%2FEfHioiJMa4qxcPep7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=a01eac63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57975298&h=597765ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180322/57975298</a>"},{"pid":"a7c9525ddeb4b5ba780fbc9955290f4e77f35f5d","tid":601044,"uid":160095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:09:29.000Z","msg":"咬穿電池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b608b8acb5dad52877bfb8a37fdc4d24b139c7","tid":601044,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7c9525ddeb4b5ba780fbc9955290f4e77f35f5d","tid":601044,"uid":160095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:09:29.000Z","msg":"咬穿電池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:11:35.000Z","msg":"當金咁來驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44a23107daa7f130eff453aae4039d6832b9278","tid":601044,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:14:03.000Z","msg":"柒到爆"},{"pid":"e212b9f5f32880525d8c61ca3f55c4fc578da4b8","tid":601044,"uid":135866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/26ueYt2FQR2A8JfSo/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F26ueYt2FQR2A8JfSo%2Fgiphy.gif&h=5a7735a4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}